          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">- or -</para>
          <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Help" styleclass="T_Menu">Help menu</link><text styleclass="T_Menu"> &gt; Download Tutorial Videos</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> </text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-weight:normal;">When the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Tutorial Video dialog box</text><text styleclass="Element"> </text><text style="font-weight:normal;">opens:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click a video in the panel on the left.</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"><text style="font-weight:normal;">Wait</text> for the video to download to your PC - see the <text styleclass="VariableName">Path</text> below.  </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">The video will play as it downloads.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">If you watch the video again, it plays directly from your PC.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Path on your PC for the Tutorial Videos:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The default path is <text styleclass="VariableName-indent">&lt;LocalAppData&gt;</text><text styleclass="VariableName">\Tutorials\</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">To specify a different directory and path:</para>
          <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Click the directory box in: <text styleclass="T_Menu">Application-Settings dialog-box &gt; General tab &gt;</text><text style="font-style:italic;"> </text><text styleclass="Separator-Header">File Options</text><text style="font-style:italic;"> &gt; </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Tutorial Video Directory</text>.<text styleclass="VariableName"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Browse to a select a different path.</li>
            <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Click the <text styleclass="VariableName">Select Folder</text> button.</li>
          </list>
